name: The Bunny and the inconceivable labyrinth
name_original: The Bunny and the inconceivable labyrinth
description:
Created for GMTK Game Jam 2020.

Guide the Bunny and her robot to the exit of the labyrinth.

It's not that simple though. You'll need to bind the robots controls first. And then rebind them when those controls inevitably run out of battery. If you run out of buttons to bind, it's all over.
